TgWsProxyNet10 is a C#/.NET 10 port inspired by Flowseal/tg-ws-proxy:
https://github.com/Flowseal/tg-ws-proxy

The original project is licensed under the MIT License:
Copyright (c) 2026 Flowseal

This repository contains a new C# implementation and does not bundle the
original Python sources, but it follows the same protocol-level idea:
local MTProto proxy -> WebSocket bridge -> Telegram DC.
